  "name": "Revamped Account Details Section",
  "body": "<p><strong>Release Date</strong> - 22nd January 2021</p>\n<h2 data-id=\"overview\">Overview</h2>\n<p>In this special release update, we bring you the spruced-up Account Details section. Explore the modernized look and experience the comfort in managing your account information; we would love to know what you think!</p>\n<h2 data-id=\"enhancements\">Enhancements</h2>\n<p><strong>Revamped Account Details</strong></p>\n<p>We simplified how you access and manage your account information. As before, the Account Details page is available in the drop-down list when you click your user name on the top-right corner of the application.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Account_Details_Nav.png\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png\" width=\"280\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 360px; width: 280px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjs.05T5g00000BkWjsEAF.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The page now consists of account-related information and tasks neatly grouped into specific tabs:</p>\n<ul><li>PROFILE – Update your profile information, login information, and profile-specific preferences. To learn more, see <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.maropost.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360015616574\">Managing Your Profile</a>.</li><li>ACCOUNT – Update your account details and settings. To learn more, see <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.maropost.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360015705613\">Managing Your Accounts</a>.</li><li>USERS – Manage your account users and their privileges. To learn more, see <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.maropost.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360017804854\">Managing Users and Their Privileges</a>.</li></ul><p>For a detailed comparison of what has changed, see <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.maropost.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360057419353\">Account Settings</a>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Profile_Tab.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/05T5g00000BkWjt.05T5g00000BkWjtEAF.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<div> </div>",
